{"id":2588,"date":"2024-12-11T17:18:07","date_gmt":"2024-12-11T17:18:07","guid":{"rendered":"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/?post_type=wiki&#038;p=2588"},"modified":"2025-01-16T20:15:10","modified_gmt":"2025-01-16T20:15:10","slug":"crater-town-gym","status":"publish","type":"wiki","link":"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/gyms\/crater-town-gym\/","title":{"rendered":"Crater Town Gym (V\u00e9ga)"},"content":{"rendered":"<p>The Crater Town Gym is the second gym you encounter in Pok\u00e9mon Unbound. V\u00e9ga, the gym leader, uses Dark-type Pok\u00e9mon. Each of his Pok\u00e9mon along with their details are showcased below:<\/p>\n<div>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\">\n<table class=\"table grey left aligntop\" style=\"min-width:500px;\">\n<thead>\n<tr>\n<th colspan=\"4\" class=\"text-large left\">Gym Leader V\u00e9ga (Vanilla)<br \/>\n        <span class=\"table-toggle\"><a href=\"#\" class=\"toggle-link\">[hide]<\/a><\/span>\n        <\/th>\n<\/tr>\n<\/thead>\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<th><\/th>\n<td><img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-content\/assets\/sprites\/pokemon\/liepard.png\" alt=\"\"><\/td>\n<td><img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-content\/assets\/sprites\/pokemon\/absol.png\" alt=\"\"><\/td>\n<td><img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-content\/assets\/sprites\/pokemon\/sneasel.png\" alt=\"\"><\/td>\n<\/tr>\n<tr>\n<th>Pokemon<\/th>\n<td>Liepard Lv. 22<\/td>\n<td>Absol Lv. 23<\/td>\n<td>Sneasel Lv. 21<\/td>\n<\/tr>\n<tr>\n<th>Type<\/th>\n<td>Dark<\/td>\n<td>Dark<\/td>\n<td>Dark \/ Ice<\/td>\n<\/tr>\n<tr>\n<th>Weaknesses<\/th>\n<td>\n<ul>\n<li>Fighting (2x)<\/li>\n<li>Bug (2x)<\/li>\n<li>Fairy (2x)<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<\/td>\n<td>\n<ul>\n<li>Fighting (2x)<\/li>\n<li>Bug (2x)<\/li>\n<li>Fairy (2x)<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<\/td>\n<td>\n<ul>\n<li>Fighting (4x)<\/li>\n<li>Rock (2x)<\/li>\n<li>Bug (2x)<\/li>\n<li>Steel (2x)<\/li>\n<li>Fire (2x)<\/li>\n<li>Fairy (2x)<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<\/td>\n<\/tr>\n<tr>\n<th>Held Item<\/th>\n<td>None<\/td